{"title":"Ruby Directory_watcher","slug":"directory_watcher","date":"2012-09-26T11:57:34.000Z","updated":"2018-04-21T08:18:25.482Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/directory_watcher.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"Useful directory wather to automatically compile or generate object files.","covers":null,"content":"<p>Useful directory wather to automatically compile or generate object files.</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"Install-Ruby-Gem\"><a href=\"#Install-Ruby-Gem\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install Ruby Gem\"></a>Install Ruby Gem</h2><pre><code>gem install directory_watcher\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"Doc-Online\"><a href=\"#Doc-Online\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Doc Online\"></a><a href=\"http://codeforpeople.rubyforge.org/directory_watcher/classes/DirectoryWatcher.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Doc Online</a></h2><h2 id=\"Source-Online\"><a href=\"#Source-Online\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Source Online\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/TwP/directory_watcher\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Source Online</a></h2><h2 id=\"Pandoc-Build-Daemon-Script\"><a href=\"#Pandoc-Build-Daemon-Script\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Pandoc Build Daemon Script\"></a>Pandoc Build Daemon Script</h2><pre><code>require &apos;directory_watcher&apos;\n\ndw = DirectoryWatcher.new &apos;.&apos;, :pre_load =&gt; true\ndw.glob = &apos;*.md&apos;\ndw.add_observer {|*args| args.each {|event| puts event}}\n\ndw.start\ngets      # when the user hits &quot;enter&quot; the script will terminate\ndw.stop\n</code></pre>","categories":[{"name":"coding","slug":"coding","count":26,"path":"api/categories/coding.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"coding","slug":"coding","count":10,"path":"api/tags/coding.json"},{"name":"ruby","slug":"ruby","count":3,"path":"api/tags/ruby.json"}]}